World Trade Center, Abuja

Reserved for the most quality-conscious leaders of society, World Trade Center, Abuja is a one-of-a-kind mixed-use development that falls nothing short of perfection.

The World Trade Center, Abuja is a mixed-use development specifically designed and built to rival major global monuments with the provision of trade services that connect Nigeria and Africa with the world. With luxurious, modern, creatively designed, and highly secure living and working spaces, it is aimed at quality-focused individuals and businesses. Its architecture is one that will transcend the years. We welcome you to explore both our ownership and leasing opportunities at the WTC Abuja.
